10.6.20  6:28 pm   yesterday i was listening to your music while laying on my bed and looking out my window at the night sky, and all of a sudden (while mount st. helens was playing, for some reason) i felt what i can only describe as a "healing stream of tingling sensations" flowing through me; and in that precise moment, for a split second, i knew. i deeply and intuitively knew that everything in existence is exactly as it should be in order to have the best possible case scenario for everything that exists, that the universe is a perfectly choreographed wholesome orchestration of artistic unconditional love; in a non-linear, harmoniously flowing, endless dance of infinite creation. then the intuition slipped away from my experience, and i was like wtf just happened? now i don't really know if there was something truly reasonable in all of that, but it was for sure an interesting experience; and i am positive that your song played a big role in it. so thank yo u for that and, finally the question part, have you ever experienced something even remotely similar while creating your music?

      take care
